            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="carousel-item">
            <p class="carousel-item-quote">
              "In my time knowing Gary, he has always looked for opportunities that were the best fit with both my experience and profile, while showing great passion for his job while always being accessible and available. I can highly recommend his excellent attitude and determination to get the best position for anyone looking for a career change."
